# Design System

## Components
- **Primary Source:** ALWAYS check `src/components/ui` for existing components (shadcn/ui) before creating new ones.
- **Composition:** Compose complex UIs using `Card`, `Dialog`, `Sheet`, etc.

## Styling (Tailwind CSS)
- **Utility First:** Use Tailwind utility classes. Avoid custom CSS modules or `style` tags.
- **Responsiveness:** Mobile-first approach. Use `sm:`, `md:`, `lg:` prefixes.
- **Spacing:** Use standard Tailwind spacing (e.g., `gap-4`, `p-6`).
- **Colors:** Use semantic colors defined in `tailwind.config.ts` (e.g., `bg-primary`, `text-muted-foreground`) rather than hardcoded hex values.

## Icons
- Use `lucide-react` for all icons.
